These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, documentary, horror
City: edinburgh, london, boston
1. the person traveling to london is in the middle##1
2. the person watching horror movies is the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | documentary | horror   |
| City      | edinburgh    | london  | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse, ferret
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, tennis, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Pet      | mouse | hedgehog     | ferret      |
| Sport   | tennis | skiing | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, pink, red
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, martial-arts, time-travel
1. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person who likes red is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Color   | coral | red  | pink       |
| Movie-Genre       | spy     | martial-arts | time-travel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, tea, iced-tea
3 different pets are kept: bird, frog, dog
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
2. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Beverage    | iced-tea    | tea     | water |
| Pet   | dog | bird | frog     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, lemonade, tea
There 3 different types of food: cherry, zucchini, pineapple
1. the person eating zucchini is the person drinking tea##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage         | lemonade | mirinda     | tea |
| Food   | pineapple        | cherry | zucchini    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, entrepreneur, journalist
House: ranch-style, townhouse, gothic-revival
1. the architect is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
2. the entrepreneur is on the right of the townhouse house##1
3. the journalist is the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Job        | journalist | architect      | entrepreneur  |
| House   | ranch-style       | townhouse | gothic-revival |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, canasta
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, bike, boat
1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing scrabble is the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Game   | canasta      | backgammon     | scrabble    |
| Transport           | motorbike | boat | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
