2. the pakistani is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
3. the chinese is the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality    | pakistani | dutch | chinese      |
| Flower   | amaryllis     | poppy | orchid |

