There 3 different types of food: grapes, apricot, tomato
1. the person eating grapes is the person playing bridge##1
2. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
