The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, handball, climbing
1. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage   | tea | lemonade   | coffee  |
| Sport   | climbing    | baseball | handball |

