There are 3 different nationalities: indian, thai, dutch
1. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
2. the dutch is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Pet      | fish  | snake | bird  |
| Nationality   | thai | dutch   | indian |

