.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-16::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, video-games, reading
House: futuristic, townhouse, cape-cod
1. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Hobby   | video-games | hiking | reading    |
| House        | futuristic    | cape-cod | townhouse |

