The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, car, train
1. the person driving the train is on the far left##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the airplane is the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Movie-Genre           | crime | superhero | romance |
| Transport   | train  | airplane      | car |

