.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
City: colone, prague, berlin
House: cottage, cape-cod, palace
1. the cape-cod house is in the middle##1
2. the palace house is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| City    | berlin | colone       | prague  |
| House   | palace  | cape-cod | cottage |

 